", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/We_Stitch_These_Wounds\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999311021407, \"rank\": 4.3163749897509756e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"owner\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 291}, {\"ngram\": \"a sweet-toothed stranger\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 350}, {\"ngram\": \"the mouthwatering double chocolate chip muffins\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 452}, {\"ngram\": \"a little-known bakery\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone wanted to taste the muffins, so I thought, 'Why not try?\\\"\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng told The Post.\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 566, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.859683640595931, \"rank\": 0.14787314974128687, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Post\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was very much a passion project and I really just wanted to try the muffins myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a passion project\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women had dozens of the treats delivered by plane for a single-day pop-up sale last Saturday at the restaurant - where locals waited in a two block-long line starting at 6 a.m. to pay $10 per muffin.\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The women\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"the treats\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"plane\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 730}, {\"ngram\": \"a single-day pop-up sale\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"the restaurant\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"a two block-long line\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"6 a.m.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"muffin\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng said they plunked down $3,000 for 300 the goodies and barely broke even - but are nevertheless planning to ship in 1,000 more.\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 882, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.859683640595931, \"rank\": 0.14787314974128687, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"300 the goodies\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The muffins became a social media star earlier this month when Norwegian swimmerHenrik Christiansenposted 10 videos raving that it was the most delicious treat in the Olympic Village dining hall.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1183, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.300689463673647e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The muffins\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"a social media star\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"10 videos\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"the most delicious treat\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other athletes, including gold medal fencing pro Lee Kiefer, called the baked good - which has huge chocolate chunks and a gooey melted chocolate center - the best thing since sliced bread.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lee Kiefer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lee_Kiefer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other athletes\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medal\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the baked good\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"huge chocolate chunks\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"a gooey melted chocolate center\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"the best thing\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"sliced bread\", \"from\": 1389, \"to\": 1401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As internet collectively salivated, the muffin earneda write-upon the food site Eater and caught the attention of Zhang, a Brooklyn-based designer who was previously unaffiliated with the cafe.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"internet\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1416}, {\"ngram\": \"write\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"the food site\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"the attention\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"a Brooklyn-based designer\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"the cafe\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang saw the videos on TikTok and became hyper-focused on tracking down and trying the muffins, shetold Gothamist, which was the first to report the story.\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.459919577691258e-40, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"the videos\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffins\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was like, OK, this seems still so much more attainable than me going to the Olympics and eating a muffin,\\\" she told Gothamist.\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1833, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"a muffin\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"Gothamist\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wanted to see if it could be done.\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I just kept going.\\\"\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Using her online sleuthing skills, she found Coup De Pates, a French food supplier whose website featured photos of what appeared to be the famous muffin.\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9247670053298404, \"rank\": 0.07970377577738537, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her online sleuthing skills\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"Coup De Pates\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"whose website\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"the famous muffin\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2109}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was later confirmed to be the viral treat by Eater.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the viral treat\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"Eater\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2164}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the bakery, located in Ferri\\u00e8res-en-Brie, has a business-to-business delivery model and wasn't set up to export food to New York.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2292, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.999350954534657, \"rank\": 0.0006494669981896049, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bakery\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"Ferri\\u00e8res-en-Brie\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"business\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So Zhang put out a call on TikTok asking to team up with a New York City restaurant in order to get them to the Big Apple, she said.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.459919577691258e-40, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}, {\"begin\": 2362, \"end\": 2375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7790816169024252e-14, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 2415, \"end\": 2424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999997453415, \"rank\": 2.545203093722153e-10, \"text\": \"Big Apple\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zhang\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2311}, {\"ngram\": \"a call\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I framed it in very capitalistic terms \\u2026 but really, I just wanted to try the muffin myself,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"very capitalistic terms\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2476}, {\"ngram\": \"the muffin\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[I wrote] 'Hey, does any restaurant or caf\\u00e9 or anything want to partner on this?\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2583, \"end\": 2587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.551169061386513e-21, \"text\": \"caf\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any restaurant\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think there is an incredible opportunity here.\\\"\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an incredible opportunity\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cafe owner saw the post and the two women joined forces.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cafe owner\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"the post\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2703}, {\"ngram\": \"the two women\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"forces\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just really just very casually was like, 'Yeah, I will do it.\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like this sounds like a fun project,'\\\" Zheng said.\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2842, \"end\": 2847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"score\": 0.859683640595931, \"rank\": 0.14787314974128687, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guzheng\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fun project\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really also for selfish reasons want to try these Olympic muffins.\\\"\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"selfish reasons\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympic muffins\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They then hounded Coup de Pates via email, phone and social media, asking the company to send the famous muffin to Isshiki Matcha on Second Avenue.\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 3073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3041, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"score\": 0.9999999810484044, \"rank\": 1.740190319196363e-08, \"text\": \"Isshiki\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isshiki_clan\"}, {\"begin\": 3049, \"end\": 3055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matcha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matcha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coup de Pates\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"email\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"phone\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\"